Hey Team, quick but big kudos to the team who worked on improving split-classification:trophy: I just live demo'd a trade finance dock I'd never seen before, and from 18 pages and 9 classes it got everything correct except one page (!even without any descriptions!). This looked super impressive and I feel much more confident in this feature now to show to customers :raised_hands:
